          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Excellent guidance and advice. Good briefings pre and post shoot. Clear joining instructions Would have appreciated more time one on one as when you get it it’s worthwhile. Acknowledge that’s hard in a group though.",
          "datePublished": ""
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
